    <p>If you like the decentraliced idea of OpenID you perhaps do like the idea of a decentralized avatar: <a href="http://pavatar.com">pavatar.com</a>. The Pavatar spec is now in Candidate Recommendation status and we need some plugins for different software.</p>
<p>Some people think OpenID and Pavatar work well together: <a href="http://brianellin.com/blog/2006/12/29/openid-pavatar-is-a-good-thing/">OpenID + Pavatar is a good thing</a> and so do I. It would be really cool to have only the one URL to log in and add your avatar automaticly on sites like Flickr, MySpace, Mo.gnolia some forums and so on.</p>
