    <p>Nice intro.  I had problems setting up the delegate to myopenid until I noticed in their docs that you need a meta tag as well as the two links.  See <a href="https://www.myopenid.com/help#own_domain" rel="nofollow">https://www.myopenid.com/help#own_domain</a></p>

